	/* * *
	 * * mixed function getPlistValue(
	 * *	  i_tag)	integer tag id whose value we seek
	 * *
	 * * companion of outputPlistArray()
	 * *
	 * * special thanks to Matsuda Shota, this is also a 'clone' of one of your functions
